thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.core
Class UVf

java.lang.Object
  thothbot.squirrel.core.shared.core.UVf

public class UVf
extends java.lang.Object

Class implements UV texture mapping. UV texturing permits polygons that make up a 3D object to be painted with color from an image. Here are: U - Horizontal coordinate. V - Vertical coordinate. UV coordinates should be applied per face. not per vertex. This means a shared vertex can have different UV coordinates in each of its triangles, so adjacent triangles can be cut apart and positioned on different areas of the texture map.

Author:
thothbot
